model.name: LV Tools Embroidered Crewneck
model.disambiguatingDescription: This chic merino wool crewneck is embellished with the SS23 Show’s playful LV Multi Tools theme. Intricately embroidered and beaded miniature tools and an LV signature form colorful pendants which stand out in graphic contrast against the chunky black knit of this eye-catching statement piece.

additionalProperty.name: detailedDescription
additionalProperty.value:
• 100% RWS-Certified Wool
  • Black
  • Cropped
  • Model wears a FR M size
  • Model measurements : chest 32’’ / 81 cm, height 6' 1½’’ / 187 cm
  • Made in Italy
